{"tid":1734614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"義務急救員哽咽稱留守理大至最後　有心理準備被捕","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T11:18:21.000Z","uid":201669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f2fbe9ca6642d3b16abe35af13961000bace529","tid":1734614,"uid":201669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/1161699934023513/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F1161699934023513%2F&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=e1650530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/1161699934023513/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n理工大學仍有一批黑衣人聚集，校園內一片凌亂，有人休息，有人商討下一步行動。現場有汽油彈遺留在正門附近，校內部分地方有煙冒出。<br />\n<br />\n有留守的中學生表示，曾經嘗試突圍，但每個街口都有防暴警察，覺得無路可退，而現場人士情緒激動，形容目前感到無助。這名中學生說，自己經常上前線，有被捕的心理準備，但沒有通知家長。<br />\n<br />\n有義務急救員表示，昨日警方不斷發射催淚彈及水炮，情況很混亂，令不少人受傷。被問到是否值得留守，他一度哽咽，並說作為義務急救員，有責任留守到最後，幫助有需要的人，強調已經做好可能被捕的心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n至於昨日警方呼籲校園內所有人循北面李兆基樓，即Y座出口離開，但部分離開的義務急救員被捕，他質疑是騙局，要令現場義務急救員及記者離開，以免外界知道對校園內對義務急救員和聚集人士的暴力情況，甚至不想傷者得到治療。"},{"pid":"a23984ed8196be1d4cc76652edd31ffc2ff2c8f0","tid":1734614,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"Twitter組24時keep住更新<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手retweet+ like + reply</span> <br />\n㩒入----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1